data.description: Discover the ultimate in suburban bliss at 8320 Timberbrook Lane, where modern living meets convenience! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath gem boasts a unique Jack and Jill en suite for the secondary bedrooms, an extended patio perfect for entertaining, and an upstairs paradise with surround sound connections. The chef-sized kitchen with its expansive island including Refrigerator and an abundance of pantry shelving will delight your culinary aspirations. Nestled on a charming corner lot, this home ensures you're less than a 20-minute commute to Downtown Dallas, with quick access to Joe Pool Lake, an array of restaurants, and shopping galore. Tour this amazing 2-story home today!
